     fold-map-fusion : fold δ (map σ M)  ≡  fold γ M

     and some specializations:

     fold-rename-fusion : fold δ (rename ρ M)  ≡ fold γ M

     fold-subst-fusion : fold δ (⟪ σ ⟫ M)  ≡ fold γ M

-}
